song.title: La Ville du Port Spatial
song.info:
After roaming several desperate months in the domains of low technology, the protagonist finally reaches a shining city where one can see huge cargo crafts landing and departing
-- information: -format: Impulse Tracker -tool: Schism Tracker -32 channels used -All the samples are emulated YM2612 instruments ripped from TFM Music Maker -The song was sent to Sundown 2014 tracked music compo but it sounded totally distorted on the stream for some reason, so I asked them to discard it
